   {"q":"Apa kelebihan kota?","options":["Udara bersih","Praktis dan banyak kesempatan","Sewa murah","Sangat sepi"],"answer":1,"explanation":"「便利で…機会も…多い」."},
   {"q":"Apa kekurangan kota?","options":["Sepi","Ramai dan biaya hidup tinggi","Tidak ada pekerjaan","Hanya udara buruk"],"answer":1,"explanation":"「人が多く…生活費がたくさんかかります」."},
   {"q":"Apa kelebihan desa?","options":["Banyak pekerjaan","Alam melimpah dan udara bersih","Transportasi murah","Banyak hiburan"],"answer":1,"explanation":"「自然が豊かで、空気がきれい」."},
   {"q":"Kenapa anak muda pindah ke kota?","options":["Bosan","Jenis pekerjaan di desa sedikit","Tidak suka alam","Karena cuaca"],"answer":1,"explanation":"「仕事の種類も少なく…都会へ出て行きます」."},
   {"q":"Apa yang terjadi pada populasi desa?","options":["Bertambah","Terus berkurang","Tetap","Berlipat ganda"],"answer":1,"explanation":"「人口が減り続けています」."}
